Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.66,0:00:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-要冲刺对吧 -绝对是要冲刺的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.80,0:00:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害的结果喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.54,0:00:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超烂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.87,0:00:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.94,0:00:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.14,0:00:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做小健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.68,0:00:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在和我一起打电动的是我的好友义彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.02,0:00:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了念大学而来到东京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.56,0:00:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在和义彦合租了一间房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.43,0:00:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那是这样啊 -很有力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.37,0:00:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.90,0:00:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是这样的吗 -真糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.30,0:00:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.04,0:00:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很糟糕耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你看看那个 -好厉害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.51,0:00:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.71,0:00:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个女孩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.32,0:00:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩是义彦的女友米亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.06,0:01:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这天她来到这间房子玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.46,0:01:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我好友大概交往了半年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.47,0:01:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是很恩爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.00,0:01:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本我想应该是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.94,0:01:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.74,0:01:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.21,0:01:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从某天开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.14,0:01:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就和好友的女友米亚有了不应该的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.62,0:01:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.22,0:01:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.29,0:01:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(傲娇的好友女友)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.23,0:01:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(在晚上三人一起睡成川字型的时候)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.30,0:01:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(扑向我与我偷情)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.91,0:01:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这样可以了吧 -可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.91,0:02:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这样不错吧 -感觉气氛不错喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还蛮开心的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.59,0:02:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这样刚好了喔 -我要烤得刚刚好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.65,0:02:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-没有焦掉喔 -没有焦掉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.86,0:02:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先给你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.72,0:02:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢 -我来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.59,0:02:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-给我吧 -要淋上去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淋上来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.26,0:02:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.86,0:02:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.80,0:02:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-自己用啦 -不要啦帮我用啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.54,0:02:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.60,0:02:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海苔粉也要加喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.87,0:02:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.74,0:02:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-帮你加啰 -谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.88,0:02:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.28,0:02:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-看起来很好吃耶 -对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会烫吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.69,0:02:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.02,0:02:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不过很好吃喔 -好烫喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.09,0:02:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.96,0:02:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这样也太随便了吧 -有吹就不错了啦 自己吹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.03,0:02:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情很好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.37,0:02:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.70,0:02:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.64,0:03:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙也交个女友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交个女友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好啊就交个女友吧 -会很恩爱的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.98,0:03:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.38,0:03:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-来嘴巴打开 -很烫啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.19,0:03:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要吹一吹再给我吃啊 很烫对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.93,0:03:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-吃这个吧 -谢谢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.67,0:03:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点焦掉了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.34,0:03:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝口酒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.87,0:03:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝酒好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝多了耶还好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.68,0:03:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很会喝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.75,0:03:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真的吗 -小健还能吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小健还吃得下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.42,0:03:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-想吃耶 -想吃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.89,0:03:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我再煎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.96,0:03:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.42,0:03:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来加章鱼啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.10,0:04:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-可是现在加太早了啦 -你是不是喝醉了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你还好吧 -讨厌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不要随便加啦 -有差吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.64,0:04:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-喂喝醉了吧 -可能是吧那拜托小健了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草鱼加进去才要再加粉浆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.78,0:04:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你看又喝多了 -你还行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-今天很想喝咩 -很想喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.05,0:04:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是这样啊 -不是要烤章鱼烧的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.12,0:04:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那拜托姊烤章鱼烧啰 -不是这样的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经蛮醉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了很开心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.67,0:04:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.27,0:04:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-已经差不多了吧 -不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 很漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.61,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样烤一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-可以转得起来吗 -可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-可以吗 -那边喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-可能很难喔 -可能可以喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下好像转得起来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.75,0:04:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-可以吗 -这边这边这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是这边吧 -用一下用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.29,0:04:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-在做什么啊 -绝对煎不好的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下是不是焦掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.76,0:05:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给它转一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-很好啊 -成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.17,0:05:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真的很圆很漂亮喔 -成功了耶 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真的成功了 -真的看起来好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个有圆吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.64,0:05:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不甘心不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个可以可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.11,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.85,0:05:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝醉了很危险不可以用喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.38,0:05:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-因为很危险喔 -看起来很好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.73,0:05:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要用哪边啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.13,0:05:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用一下 用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.26,0:05:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很好很好很好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好像 -你还醒着吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-醒着喔 -真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-还好吗  -有焦掉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还好喔 有点焦掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边喔 很好很好很好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃哪个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃哪个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-感觉很好喔 -睡着了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.16,0:06:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小义啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.23,0:06:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-喂喂 -竟然睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚脸就很红了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.97,0:06:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能喝多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很对不起章鱼烧喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.04,0:06:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.44,0:06:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没什么帮倒忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.12,0:06:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-小义啊 -你没醒着吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.72,0:06:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有听到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的睡着了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.06,0:06:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以在这边睡觉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.40,0:06:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.54,0:06:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你去睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.47,0:06:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都喝光了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.07,0:06:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为喝多了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.61,0:06:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这个姿势睡着了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.95,0:07:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体会痛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.55,0:07:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-去那边睡啦 -哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.82,0:07:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.89,0:07:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-小义很危险喔 要小心喔 -要注意喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那个没关系吗 -没关系喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.89,0:07:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.56,0:07:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啊走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小义你还好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊慢慢下去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.97,0:07:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你一下
