Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:00.78,0:42:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然和好友的女友米亚做爱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:07.45,0:42:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说幸运也是幸运啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:11.06,0:42:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我想还是不好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:15.46,0:42:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那家伙感觉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:18.40,0:42:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:21.07,0:42:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米亚好像也不怎么在意耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:24.94,0:42:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像装成没做过一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:32.95,0:42:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小义啊 今天大学放学后要去哪边啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:37.62,0:42:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-要不要做豆沙包给我吃啊 -小义你做啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:42.02,0:42:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米亚你做啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:43.62,0:42:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那一起做吧 -好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:46.83,0:42:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么啦都没吃饭耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:52.03,0:42:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好吃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:53.50,0:42:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:54.83,0:42:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以不用勉强吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:56.70,0:42:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:57.64,0:42:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小义吃了很多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:59.77,0:43:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:01.11,0:43:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想之后要做什么好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:05.24,0:43:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-小义什么都觉得好吃啊 -很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:08.85,0:43:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我会煮饭煮得很开心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:23.13,0:43:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:27.13,0:43:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:29.27,0:43:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以去一下厕所吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:30.87,0:43:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:32.47,0:43:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:33.54,0:43:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以先去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:35.14,0:43:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 我等你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:36.08,0:43:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 那你等一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:38.08,0:43:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:41.28,0:43:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.49,0:43:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:07.31,0:44:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:09.31,0:44:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要做这种事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:11.31,0:44:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:13.85,0:44:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:15.31,0:44:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:17.45,0:44:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊不行不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:19.72,0:44:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:23.32,0:44:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:27.19,0:44:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:29.60,0:44:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:31.60,0:44:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能不去了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:34.40,0:44:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:41.07,0:44:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小健啊还没好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:44.94,0:44:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:46.28,0:44:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会迟到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:47.88,0:44:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我知道啦 -你这家伙在做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:51.35,0:44:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:54.55,0:44:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-再等一下喔 -会迟到喔 你在做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:05.10,0:45:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:08.30,0:45:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很糟糕啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:11.10,0:45:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:20.58,0:45:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等 不要啊 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:30.46,0:45:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么激烈的话很糟糕啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:42.60,0:45:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:44.07,0:45:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 要射了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:03.16,0:46:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:07.83,0:46:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经受不了了啊 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:10.36,0:46:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:14.10,0:46:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了啊去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:48.80,0:46:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:53.87,0:46:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也做爱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:56.81,0:46:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要对小义保密喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:48.59,0:47:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来是没有想帮你口交的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:57.27,0:47:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是刚刚觉得你很可爱而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:16.22,0:48:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起洗澡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:19.29,0:48:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 不是讨厌啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:22.76,0:48:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是害羞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:24.50,0:48:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:26.10,0:48:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:27.57,0:48:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个这样做 会对那家伙很抱歉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:33.44,0:48:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是不好的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:36.78,0:48:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:38.51,0:48:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被发现的话有什么关系啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:43.85,0:48:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小义现在在打电动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:47.99,0:48:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概不会被发现的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:51.99,0:48:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:55.73,0:48:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:58.26,0:49:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:01.33,0:49:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我不是把你搞成小义做爱了对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:06.94,0:49:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:10.14,0:49:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:11.61,0:49:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:22.15,0:49:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转过来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:48.71,0:49:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来洗身体吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:52.18,0:49:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:54.45,0:49:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:02.33,0:50:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:06.33,0:50:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真的要吗 -手伸出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:07.80,0:50:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:09.67,0:50:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了就这样来洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:12.74,0:50:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:14.87,0:50:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗真的可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:19.41,0:50:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:26.89,0:50:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好洗喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:29.55,0:50:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:41.03,0:50:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好好洗喔 -好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:55.18,0:50:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:58.12,0:50:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换我帮你洗喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:00.92,0:51:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:02.79,0:51:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:08.26,0:51:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你洗干净喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:12.80,0:51:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好棒啊 -为什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:16.40,0:51:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个变大了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:25.61,0:51:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好棒啊 -亲亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:40.43,0:51:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起洗澡好开心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:48.97,0:51:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以洗这边吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:18.86,0:52:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:32.74,0:52:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:35.01,0:52:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:47.03,0:52:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:53.30,0:52:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小健在洗澡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:55.83,0:52:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:58.64,0:53:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-小健啊 -我在洗在洗澡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:01.04,0:53:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊我也要洗喔 热水不用放掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:22.53,0:53:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-吓我一跳 -好险喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:50.96,0:53:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:52.96,0:53:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这边喔 -这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:04.97,0:54:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很紧张耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:11.11,0:54:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想说会被发现了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:14.71,0:54:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这样不好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:25.92,0:54:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这样会射喔 -不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:30.20,0:54:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:50.22,0:54:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样用的话会射喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:59.02,0:55:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了惨了 要射了要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:01.29,0:55:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要射了 停下来停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:03.56,0:55:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:17.04,0:55:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:31.59,0:55:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射了好多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:37.46,0:55:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你要一起洗到什么时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:42.13,0:55:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一直被看不好啦 快点出去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:47.61,0:55:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要保密喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:51.21,0:55:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:52.34,0:56:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:02.08,0:57:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:14.09,0:57:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起吵醒你了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:18.23,0:57:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:25.57,0:57:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我睡不着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:33.18,0:57:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以一起睡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:42.52,0:57:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让我好好睡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:52.72,0:58:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:09.01,0:59:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以舔这边吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:20.35,0:59:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以出声喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:42.83,1:00:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么翘得这么硬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:52.71,1:00:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为米亚这样兴奋了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:00.59,1:01:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:16.60,1:01:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:29.41,1:01:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:31.42,1:01:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:42.89,1:01:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸我奶子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:58.11,1:02:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热喔 都流汗了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:20.13,1:02:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想看下面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:25.74,1:02:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:28.54,1:02:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保密喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:06.71,1:03:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:35.27,1:03:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这么湿了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:19.85,1:04:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:02.69,1:05:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插进来罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:32.46,1:05:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:59.82,1:06:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:25.31,1:06:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法啊 因为睡不着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:33.85,1:06:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要满足我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:00.95,1:07:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小健的鸡鸡插进妹妹里啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:15.89,1:07:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:33.91,1:07:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:43.12,1:07:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在米亚说可以之前不可以射喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:55.80,1:07:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:00.07,1:08:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:14.75,1:08:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:53.32,1:08:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这边来做喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:56.66,1:08:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从后面插进来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:01.07,1:09:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我鸡鸡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:33.76,1:09:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:40.04,1:09:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服啊
